{"tid":293954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴本月底引入新紅色巴士　有12個USB充電插座","createTime":"2017-06-22T14:36:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T16:04:31.000Z","uid":48093,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"86b32273b8a413046f92e02ad55c88eea8a19c5a","tid":293954,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T14:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1337731_1_L_20170622223111.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1337731_1_L_20170622223111.jpg&h=39eaec03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九巴新一代巴士預計本月底開始投入服務，車上新增無線上網裝置，每輛巴士會有12個USB充電插座。<br />\n<br />\n約70輛紅色車身的新九巴車隊，年底會陸續到港。"},{"pid":"fab1d21c7024f414532b918193b9cdbd5ab0ef0b","tid":293954,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T14:38:22.000Z","msg":"點分？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又人性的考驗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1dea73de260d70a4b72107a226fbb512c16ff4d","tid":293954,"uid":43809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T14:41:20.000Z","msg":"又有電話執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e03ccd582a3604218c463712a3251999df34d1","tid":293954,"uid":80107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T14:41:44.000Z","msg":"關愛插座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4ceeb4d6fbfefd61b3b7d08a2cc7d0cffad961","tid":293954,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:13:20.000Z","msg":"被問到新一代巴士的成本，九巴策劃及發展部襄理梁領彥說，新一代巴士的底盤與現有的一樣，分別只在於車身設計，因此價錢相若。<br />\n<br />\n九巴計劃下半年為大約一千輛巴士完成安裝免費無線上網裝置，並計劃於未來數年內為二千輛巴士，即約一半車隊提供有關服務。<br />\n<br />\n梁領彥表示，聽取市民意見後，新一代巴士的USB充電插座將會由原定的兩個，增添至十二個，讓更多乘客可於旅途中為手機充電。但有司機表示，擔心USB充電插座數量不足，會導致乘客有爭執。"},{"pid":"6e64f04e52b3e76e140fe50ccc9d6314cf83514e","tid":293954,"uid":114193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:15:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n城巴新巴真係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e71734e3744d2b6da9219034e5c31a0ccb4daf1","tid":293954,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:15:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點分？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又人性的考驗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到時網民熱話  廢青 唔讓叉電位比老人  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83fb7b326cca9856a61e23007847a030f55817e4","tid":293954,"uid":30476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:16:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>被問到新一代巴士的成本，九巴策劃及發展部襄理梁領彥說，新一代巴士的底盤與現有的一樣，分別只在於車身設計，因此價錢相若。<br />\n<br />\n九巴計劃下半年為大約一千輛巴士完成安裝免費無線上網裝置，並計劃於未來數年內為二千輛巴士，即約一半車隊提供有關服務。<br />\n<br />\n梁領彥表示，聽取市民意見後，新一代巴士的USB充電插座將會由原定的兩個，增添至十二個，讓更多乘客可於旅途中為手機充電。但有司機表示，擔心USB充電插座數量不足，會導致乘客有爭執。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港人用一個月可能已經壞哂"},{"pid":"83e7e46179b2ce939a9fe41c3c8c9492b653830c","tid":293954,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:19:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>被問到新一代巴士的成本，九巴策劃及發展部襄理梁領彥說，新一代巴士的底盤與現有的一樣，分別只在於車身設計，因此價錢相若。<br />\n<br />\n九巴計劃下半年為大約一千輛巴士完成安裝免費無線上網裝置，並計劃於未來數年內為二千輛巴士，即約一半車隊提供有關服務。<br />\n<br />\n梁領彥表示，聽取市民意見後，新一代巴士的USB充電插座將會由原定的兩個，增添至十二個，讓更多乘客可於旅途中為手機充電。但有司機表示，擔心USB充電插座數量不足，會導致乘客有爭執。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港人用一個月可能已經壞哂</blockquote><br />\n香口膠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd972b3613ec85ab7792d178a5e5102efd8a4e97","tid":293954,"uid":42536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:22:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點分？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又人性的考驗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到時網民熱話  廢青 唔讓叉電位比老人  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n關愛(充電)座"},{"pid":"6a0bc6c6495b948d886be53b725158ae61caeb56","tid":293954,"uid":76148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:24:00.000Z","msg":"香囗膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d503c49fb51e8eb654713dc41ac8ee2a36b7dcb","tid":293954,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:27:30.000Z","msg":"新車亦增設12個USB充電插座，分設於上、下層後座位置及輪椅停泊位，九巴方面解釋，充電位設於後座是希望鼓勵市民上車後「行入點」，不要堵塞在通道，善用巴士空間。<br />\n<br />\n另外，九巴正推行試驗項目，利用科技在巴士下層提供上層空座實時資訊，減少市民不必要上落。"},{"pid":"7bc51c6bee297a5a671c54535a37eefaf4deaa67","tid":293954,"uid":37136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:31:00.000Z","msg":"如果唔覺意插左隻usb killer落去會點呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9470267a8ae82f7eafe8e6fec798125a6a9d3ca5","tid":293954,"uid":69994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:35:44.000Z","msg":"好簡易既推理 , 提款機有CAM咁高難度都有人做手腳偷提款卡資料<br />\n手提電話呢個年代等如電子錢包 , 周圍插好易中毒 , USB好難防 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cafd2b58e968854c896a73ed2483c09e77408476","tid":293954,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:35:47.000Z","msg":"好快會比人整壞晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac5bbc5558eee93373f902f2298150b031935d73","tid":293954,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:38:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好快會比人整壞晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>就算唔壞都唔想用<br />\n感覺上好污糟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1658b9f54388f3fedaa55a88bb823e5bab0c2708","tid":293954,"uid":4609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:38:07.000Z","msg":"如果好快越哂 只可証明香港人文明差到極點"},{"pid":"65053f93a34b589cd5748b9f4d3a950908c96bf1","tid":293954,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:39:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果好快越哂 只可証明香港人文明差到極點</blockquote>未必<br />\n可能係弱智／盲 唔識睇方向暴力強入硬插 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daaef0598c3dcf58a74e6c40ae64abb35772e5ba","tid":293954,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:41:19.000Z","msg":"個10a狀元30歲已經做經理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e987dbce8cf8e9b9a38c69390720e7ae7d70b6e7","tid":293954,"uid":115042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:47:30.000Z","msg":"好快巴士車廂內顏色同車身一樣,<br />\n係血紅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c7f8cef5402b74ea9592be3f31c78272b0482ae","tid":293954,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:55:06.000Z","msg":"上層扶手幾乎「絕跡」，改為收納在座椅頭枕旁，減少碰撞。新一代九巴設有十二個USB充電插頭，主要設於下層輪椅人士座位及車尾位置，讓乘客乘車時都可以充電。<br />\n<br />\n九巴指充電插頭設在車尾位置，是希望鼓勵乘客上車後「行入點」。新車亦提供免費無線上網服務。<br />\n<br />\n首批三輛「紅巴」月底率先投入服務，分別行走市區1A路線，及來往港島和屯門及北區的960和978過海路線。<br />\n<br />\n九巴策劃及發展部襄理梁領彥表示：「主要希望這些路線，可以接觸多些不同區分，譬如1A在九龍市區，其實會經過觀塘區、黃大仙、九龍城，亦經過油尖旺，差不多大部分區域都會去，可以接觸多些市民。」"},{"pid":"5acd6fa15d79e93e07fb1ab96e101f90a4a7a1c5","tid":293954,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:56:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果唔覺意插左隻usb killer落去會點呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做乜撚嘢"},{"pid":"bc22ac113c17c7e9d124a415938fded3cf39197d","tid":293954,"uid":35365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:56:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個10a狀元30歲已經做經理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你估真係請件10a渣巴士咁浪費咩<br />\n之前搞gimmick野姐"},{"pid":"37c1a3ce45b5b12d826022992f8c48a38f762cb5","tid":293954,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:58:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個10a狀元30歲已經做經理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你估真係請件10a渣巴士咁浪費咩<br />\n之前搞gimmick野姐</blockquote><br />\n成為了車長的Gary在過了6個月試用期後，即被九巴建議兼任策劃及發展部工作，仕途平步青雲；當時不少網民都認為Gary很快會離開九巴，但至今工作已近4年的他未離職；九巴回覆《香港01》查詢指，Gary現時在九巴策劃及發展部任職襄理（經理），一星期會有一至兩天擔當車長職務；記者從Gary個人Facebook可見，他日前亦有駕駛103線；同時，又或者因其形象好，九巴亦經常找他做「生招牌」，不時出現在九巴的Facebook進行直播，更在招募車長廣告中擔任模特兒。"},{"pid":"00a1eb94bc4078a4b21c121c686f3b69a5dd1b3c","tid":293954,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T16:04:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1841727/City Red 紅巴初體驗 九巴仔拜拜！9 大新車的秘密\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1841727%2FCity%20Red%20%E7%B4%85%E5%B7%B4%E5%88%9D%E9%AB%94%E9%A9%97%20%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E4%BB%94%E6%8B%9C%E6%8B%9C%EF%BC%819%20%E5%A4%A7%E6%96%B0%E8%BB%8A%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86&d=EUjDLDDMX5U%2B3TANqbjGCf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=7e03867d\" target=\"_blank\">http://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1841727/City Red 紅巴初體驗 九巴仔拜拜！9 大新車的秘密</a>"}]}